# ── What IS committed (everything else) ──────────────────────────────────────
# data/processed/      ← feature parquets (built from raw, small enough)
# models/              ← trained model files + metrics + eval_history.json
# predictions/         ← prediction JSONs
# src/                 ← all Python source files
# .streamlit/          ← Streamlit config
# requirements.txt